{"tid":1390872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港懲教仲有幾大容量？","createTime":"2019-07-31T09:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:32:42.000Z","uid":280615,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"33b2facc9687965ccc7f9c1970cf8dd13e118ead","tid":1390872,"uid":280615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"//There are 29 correctional facilities in Hong Kong, which can accommodate up to 8,400 people in total. These include 24 correctional institutions, three half-way houses and two custodial wards of public hospitals.// <a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/2077873/hong-kongs-prison-system-explained\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Farticle%2F2077873%2Fhong-kongs-prison-system-explained&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=ab3378f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/2077873/hong-kongs-prison-system-explained</a><br />\n<br />\n香港加埋曬都係得8400個位，仲要有啲位俾rehabilitation centres take up 左。但係根據懲教網頁，已經用左8241個位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csd.gov.hk/tc_chi/statistics/statistics_on_number_of_persons_in_custody_by_institution.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fstatistics%2Fstatistics_on_number_of_persons_in_custody_by_institution.html&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=4f40a5b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csd.gov.hk/tc_chi/statistics/statistics_on_number_of_persons_in_custody_by_institution.html</a><br />\n<br />\n理論上佢仲有160個位，佢再嚟多幾次大規模搜捕就會逼爆監房？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP牌仔第一次開post，有講錯請多多見諒！"},{"pid":"d2ac5d5bcea4e397bb84f98a3bc1017ff585688f","tid":1390872,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></